Package org.knime.core.webui.node.dialog.defaultdialog.persistence.field

Interface FieldNodeSettingsPersistor<T>

Type Parameters:
T - type of object loaded by the persistor
All Superinterfaces:
NodeSettingsPersistor<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
FSLocationPersistor, LegacyColumnFilterPersistor, NodeSettingsPersistorWithConfigKey, SelectionCheckboxesToSelectionModePersistor, StringArrayToColumnFilterPersistor, StringToColumnSelectionPersistor
public interface FieldNodeSettingsPersistor<T> extends NodeSettingsPersistor<T>
A NodeSettingsPersistor that persists a single field of a settings object. Implementing classes must provide all config keys which are used via the getConfigKeys() method.
Author:
Benjamin Wilhelm, KNIME GmbH, Berlin, Germany
